    "By making education more personalized, effective, and accessible, platforms like LEAP are paving the way for a new era in educational technology.",
    "Although LEAP shows great potential, certain limitations remain.",
    "A key challenge is to ensure the accuracy and reliability of AI-generated feedback for a wide range of tasks, as LLMs can occasionally produce biased or erroneous results.",
    "In addition, the overall effectiveness of formative feedback provided by LLMs remains to be conclusively clarified.",
    "Future research should aim to fill these gaps by providing more practical insights and validating the impact of AI-driven feedback on student learning outcomes."
